    <item>
      <title>美国页岩油生产商尽管承诺克制，但仍增加产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/us-shale-producers-to-boost-output-despite-pledging-restraint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些美国领先的页岩油生产商计划今年开采更多石油，超出最初的预期，这表明全国供应量可能超过许多公司承诺的温和增长预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/us-shale-producers-to-boost-output-despite-pledging-restraint</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:50:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
